{"words":[{"word":"i'd","count":3},{"word":"bye-bye","count":2},{"word":"everyone","count":2},{"word":"huh","count":2},{"word":"anything","count":2},{"word":"calith","count":2},{"word":"into","count":2},{"word":"looked","count":2},{"word":"play","count":2},{"word":"natural","count":2},{"word":"phew","count":1},{"word":"finally","count":1},{"word":"job","count":1},{"word":"done","count":1},{"word":"complicated","count":1},{"word":"beef","count":1},{"word":"backup","count":1},{"word":"called","count":1},{"word":"owed","count":1},{"word":"small","count":1},{"word":"favor","count":1},{"word":"square","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"special","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"shift","count":1},{"word":"ran","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"bugging","count":1},{"word":"asked","count":1},{"word":"curiosity","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"insisting","count":1},{"word":"peaks","count":1},{"word":"prestige","count":1},{"word":"game","count":1},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"haha","count":1},{"word":"wanted","count":1},{"word":"fan","count":1},{"word":"club","count":1},{"word":"figured","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"pay","count":1},{"word":"sigh","count":1},{"word":"known","count":1},{"word":"hassle","count":1},{"word":"would've","count":1},{"word":"since","count":1},{"word":"lost","count":1},{"word":"guess","count":1},{"word":"cut","count":1},{"word":"complain","count":1},{"word":"course","count":1},{"word":"hate","count":1},{"word":"requires","count":1},{"word":"effort","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"getting","count":1},{"word":"dragged","count":1},{"word":"errands","count":1},{"word":"boss","count":1},{"word":"professor","count":1},{"word":"academy","count":1},{"word":"attack","count":1},{"word":"voidworms","count":1},{"word":"td","count":1},{"word":"outbreak","count":1},{"word":"gladly","count":1},{"word":"put","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"line","count":1},{"word":"protect","count":1},{"word":"kind","count":1},{"word":"meaningless","count":1},{"word":"scut","count":1},{"word":"work","count":1},{"word":"thanks","count":1},{"word":"mention","count":1},{"word":"better","count":1},{"word":"going","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Phew... Finally. My job here is done.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"That's it for me. Bye-bye, everyone.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Huh? We don't have some complicated beef or anything... I was just backup Calith called in.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Owed him a small favor, and now we're square. Come on, just let me go.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Huh? Nothing special, really. I was on shift when I ran into Calith, and it looked like something was bugging him. I asked out of curiosity.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Next thing I know, he's insisting I play Peaks of Prestige with him. After one game, he said I was a natural. Haha... do I look like a natural to you?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"He wanted me to play against this fan club. I figured it'd be a good way to pay him back too.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Sigh... If I'd known it'd be this much of a hassle, I would've just looked the other way. But since I lost, guess I wasn't cut out for it. He can't complain.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Of course not. I hate anything that requires effort. And I'm always getting dragged into errands by my boss or some professor.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"If the Academy were under attack by Voidworms or a TD outbreak, I'd gladly put my life on the line to protect everyone.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"But this kind of meaningless scut work? No thanks.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Don't mention it... Well, I'd better get going. Bye-bye.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019}]}